{"id": "51687", "revid": "2011810", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51687", "title": "Unending Storm", "text": " is the eighth major update for \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". It released on May 23, 2024.\nFeatures.\nParagon rewards.\nAfter the update, players' Paragon levels were compressed from a maximum of 1400 to 300. The Server Paragon Level became 270. Players received a one-time reward of &lt;a href=\"Crests\"&gt;Rare and Legendary Crests&lt;/a&gt; based on the Paragon level they had before the update.\nThe squish ratio for Paragon levels of 1400 and above is 1. This can be seen in some interface elements that still display the pre-compression level, such as the &lt;a href=\"Rite%20of%20Exile\"&gt;Rite of Exile&lt;/a&gt; sign-up interface and the information button next to the player's level on their profile page."}
{"id": "21434", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=21434", "title": "Unending War", "text": "Unending War is a &lt;a href=\"Crafted%20items\"&gt;crafted&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Two-Handed%20Mighty%20Weapons\"&gt;Two-Handed Mighty Weapon&lt;/a&gt; for the in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 23 to be equipped. The level 70 crafted equivalent is &lt;a href=\"War%20of%20the%20Dead\"&gt;War of the Dead&lt;/a&gt;.\nCrafting.\nUnending War can be crafted using the Plan: Unending War, 6000 &lt;a href=\"gold\"&gt;gold&lt;/a&gt;, 15 &lt;a href=\"Reusable%20Parts\"&gt;Reusable Parts&lt;/a&gt;, 15 &lt;a href=\"Arcane%20Dust\"&gt;Arcane Dust&lt;/a&gt; and 10 &lt;a href=\"Veiled%20Crystal\"&gt;Veiled Crystal&lt;/a&gt;s."}
