{"id": "49326", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49326", "title": "Darkened Holt", "text": "Darkened Holt is a campaign-only in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\nThe Darkened Holt is located in &lt;a href=\"Mistral%20Woods\"&gt;Mistral Woods&lt;/a&gt;. It is shrouded in a &lt;a href=\"magic\"&gt;magic&lt;/a&gt;al mist created by the &lt;a href=\"Horadrim\"&gt;Horadrim&lt;/a&gt;, in order to waylay those who enter its forested paths. The trail to the &lt;a href=\"Horadric%20Vault\"&gt;Horadric Vault&lt;/a&gt; heads through the Darkened Holt.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231336\"&gt;1336&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Neyrelle\"&gt;Neyrelle&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Vhenard\"&gt;Vhenard&lt;/a&gt; entered the Holt, but were forced to turn back as the mists surrounded them. Later, Neyrelle re-entered the Holt, and so did . The Wanderer found themselves lost in the mists, but was guided by the &lt;a href=\"Bloodied%20Wolf\"&gt;Bloodied Wolf&lt;/a&gt;, who through the use of portals, allowed them to reunite with Neyrelle.\nIn-game.\nThe Darkened Holt is encountered in of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20IV\"&gt;Diablo IV&lt;/a&gt;\", during the &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; \"&lt;a href=\"Shroud%20of%20the%20Horadrim\"&gt;Shroud of the Horadrim&lt;/a&gt;.\" After it is completed, it cannot be re-accessed."}
