{"id": "33275", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=33275", "title": "Deathwish", "text": "Deathwish\u00a0is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"sword\"&gt;sword&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\", one of the five &lt;a href=\"Quinblades\"&gt;Quinblades&lt;/a&gt;, added in patch 2.4.0 (though it was present in game files since patch 2.1). It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a070 to drop.\nThe unique affix boosts all channeled &lt;a href=\"Wizard\"&gt;Wizard&lt;/a&gt; skills, increasing their damage output multiplicatively. Other damage sources benefit from it as well, though it may be hard to use them simultaneously with channeling a skill (though &lt;a href=\"Etched%20Sigil\"&gt;Etched Sigil&lt;/a&gt; solves that issue).\nAs of patch 2.6.8, the effect only works after 1 second of channeling."}
