{"id": "34805", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=34805", "title": "Decrepify (Diablo III)", "text": "Decrepify is a Curse skill in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\", functioning similarly to &lt;a href=\"Weaken\"&gt;Weaken&lt;/a&gt; and from the previous game (though it does not reduce &lt;a href=\"Physical\"&gt;Physical&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"resistance\"&gt;resistance&lt;/a&gt; anymore).\nIn-game.\nWhen activated, this skill curses the ground within the targeted area for 1 second. Any enemy touched by it will be cursed for 30 seconds.\nUnlike \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\" Curses, in \"Diablo III\" multiple curses can afflict the same target."}
