{"id": "9184", "revid": "24916843", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=9184", "title": "Deep Freeze", "text": "Deep Freeze was a passive &lt;a href=\"Wizard\"&gt;Wizard&lt;/a&gt; skill in early builds of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It would increase the &lt;a href=\"critical%20hit\"&gt;critical hit&lt;/a&gt; chance of &lt;a href=\"cold\"&gt;cold&lt;/a&gt; spells by 5% and make all critical hits &lt;a href=\"freeze\"&gt;freeze&lt;/a&gt; target.\nThis skill was eventually removed from the game, with &lt;a href=\"Cold%20Blooded\"&gt;Cold Blooded&lt;/a&gt; and some &lt;a href=\"skill%20runes\"&gt;skill runes&lt;/a&gt; partially reincorporating its effect."}
