{"id": "26905", "revid": "25771421", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=26905", "title": "Defender of Westmarch", "text": "Defender of Westmarch\u00a0is a\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;Legendary&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0&lt;a href=\"shields\"&gt;shield&lt;/a&gt; in\u00a0\"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It requires\u00a0&lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt;\u00a031 to drop.\nThe special affix creates a small spectral wolf, essentially a slow piercing missile that travels for roughly 60 yards. The wolf is charging at the random enemy in vicinity, not necessarily in the direction the bearer is facing.\nAs of patch 2.4.3, it can no longer summon a wolf more than once per second, but damage done by the wolf is increased for each block made during the interim.\n&lt;a href=\"Lord%20Wynton\"&gt;Lord Wynton&lt;/a&gt; carries this shield in combat."}
