{"id": "52212", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=52212", "title": "Demon Souls", "text": "Demon Souls is an &lt;a href=\"Event%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;event&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Act%20V%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act V&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\". It takes place in &lt;a href=\"Pandemonium%20Fortress\"&gt;Pandemonium Fortress&lt;/a&gt; Level 1, and a &lt;a href=\"bounty\"&gt;bounty&lt;/a&gt; may be offered to complete it.\n&lt;a href=\"Jamella\"&gt;Jamella&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Halbu\"&gt;Halbu&lt;/a&gt;, the only two long-term mortal residents of the Fortress during the events of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20II\"&gt;Diablo II&lt;/a&gt;\", have been slain in Malthael's takeover, but they linger as ghosts. Jamella greets &lt;a href=\"The%20Nephalem\"&gt;The Nephalem&lt;/a&gt; with her iconic \"Hail to you, champion\", and they warn of more &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Crucible\"&gt;Soul Crucible&lt;/a&gt;s being used by &lt;a href=\"Malthael\"&gt;Malthael&lt;/a&gt; to fuel his power, but in this case with the souls of demons being executed within the Fortress.\nThe hero must destroy the crucibles, guarded by &lt;a href=\"Winged%20Assassin\"&gt;Winged Assassin&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"Anarch\"&gt;Anarch&lt;/a&gt;s, and then the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Scavenger\"&gt;Soul Scavenger&lt;/a&gt; channeling the souls to Malthael. Each objective is on a different isolated platform, but at each stage of the event, short-range Death Gate portals like those elsewhere in the Fortress appear as necessary. A brief thanks from Jamella completes the event, awarding gold and experience. The ghosts remain after it is done."}
