{"id": "51705", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=51705", "title": "Moonrite Divination", "text": " is a service offered by &lt;a href=\"Nisza\"&gt;Nisza&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"adventurer\"&gt;adventurer&lt;/a&gt;s in &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20%28City%29\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt;. Using her scrying pool, one can divine present/upcoming major threats.\nIn-game.\n is available at Nisza's stand in Westmarch. The vision seen in the scrying pool is a 35 second cinematic that offers spoilers for the next major update of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\", and remains till the onset of the next update. The pool so far have shown visions of the &lt;a href=\"Southern%20Dreadlands\"&gt;Southern Dreadlands&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Terror%20Rift\"&gt;Terror Rift&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Abyssal%20Verge\"&gt;Abyssal Verge&lt;/a&gt;s, &lt;a href=\"Riven%20Shade\"&gt;Riven Shade&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"the%20Unmaking\"&gt;the Unmaking&lt;/a&gt;, corresponding with the \"&lt;a href=\"Splintered%20Souls\"&gt;Splintered Souls&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Precipice%20of%20Horror\"&gt;Precipice of Horror&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Unending%20Storm\"&gt;Unending Storm&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Crucible%20of%20Justice\"&gt;Crucible of Justice&lt;/a&gt;\" and \"&lt;a href=\"Shattered%20Sanctuary\"&gt;Shattered Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt;\" updates."}
