{"id": "41140", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=41140", "title": "Mount Zavain", "text": "Mount Zavain is a mountain in the northern region of the &lt;a href=\"Tamoe%20Mountains\"&gt;Tamoe Mountain Range&lt;/a&gt;. A port is located near the mountain, from where one can travel to it with a caravan.\nLore.\nMount Zavain was soaked in &lt;a href=\"blood\"&gt;blood&lt;/a&gt; long ago in &lt;a href=\"Zakarum%20Crusade\"&gt;a war&lt;/a&gt; between the &lt;a href=\"Sons%20of%20Rakkis\"&gt;Sons of Rakkis&lt;/a&gt; and the &lt;a href=\"Veradani\"&gt;Veradani&lt;/a&gt;. By &lt;a href=\"Timeline%231270\"&gt;1270&lt;/a&gt;, the war's scars still clung to Zavain's people. To make matters worse, &lt;a href=\"khazra\"&gt;khazra&lt;/a&gt; activity had surged, the goatmen displaying new intelligence and maleficence. Deep &lt;a href=\"Black%20Mists\"&gt;black fog&lt;/a&gt; spread through &lt;a href=\"Misty%20Valley\"&gt;the valleys&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Cult%20of%20Damnation\"&gt;damnation&lt;/a&gt; festered in the mountain's shadow, and it was believed that it was only a matter of time before the overwhelmed and underequipped soldiers of &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%27s%20Watch\"&gt;Sentinel's Watch&lt;/a&gt; were swallowed up.\nLater, foreboding black mist began to emanate from the &lt;a href=\"Silent%20Monastery\"&gt;Silent Monastery&lt;/a&gt;, threatening to cover the entire mountain in darkness.\nIn-game.\nMount Zavain is a zone in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\". It is accessible after &lt;a href=\"Bilefen\"&gt;Bilefen&lt;/a&gt;. The player must be at least &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;level&lt;/a&gt; 46 to access its &lt;a href=\"quest\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt;line."}
{"id": "46437", "revid": "50366882", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=46437", "title": "Mountain Path", "text": " is the path that connects the portal to &lt;a href=\"Westmarch%20%28City%29\"&gt;Westmarch&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%27s%20Watch\"&gt;Sentinel's Watch&lt;/a&gt;. It is the beginning of the &lt;a href=\"Mount%20Zavain\"&gt;Mount Zavain&lt;/a&gt; zone in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\n leads from a nearby port to the &lt;a href=\"Foggy%20Plains\"&gt;plains&lt;/a&gt; of Mount Zavain. Caravans bringing supplies from Westmarch use this route to get up the mountain."}
