{"id": "49707", "revid": "58609", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=49707", "title": "Myrrjen", "text": "The Myrrjen is a &lt;a href=\"Familiar%20%28Diablo%20Immortal%29\"&gt;Familiar&lt;/a&gt; introduced in \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20Immortal\"&gt;Diablo Immortal&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\nWidely considered a myth, Myrrjen are often blamed for all manner of nautical problems from broken anchors to poor weather. In truth, they are curious, playful spirits that inhabit the depths of &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary\"&gt;Sanctuary&lt;/a&gt;'s oceans. They have been known to venture to the surface from time to time to amuse themselves watching passing ships, and conjuring raging storms in their paths."}
