{"id": "20112", "revid": "1773829", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20112", "title": "Mysterious Cave", "text": "The Mysterious Cave is a two-floor cave\u00a0in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Dahlgur%20Oasis\"&gt;Dahlgur Oasis&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Act%20II%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Act II&lt;/a&gt; of \"&lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nIt\u00a0can spawn in one of the two watered-in nooks in Dahlgur Oasis, both of which extend south from the open parts of the zone. The southern one is east of the entrance from the &lt;a href=\"Ruined%20Cistern\"&gt;Ruined Cistern&lt;/a&gt;, and the northern one is east of the \"neck\" that connects the north and south halves of the zone. The cave can only be opened by helping &lt;a href=\"Zaven%20the%20Alchemist\"&gt;Zaven the Alchemist&lt;/a&gt; fend off a few angry &lt;a href=\"Wraith%20%28Diablo%20III%29\"&gt;Wraiths&lt;/a&gt;, after which he opens the cave and lets the player enter. This area must be explored in order to complete the achievement\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Nooks%20and%20Crannies\"&gt;Nooks and Crannies&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe cave may contain a Mysterious Chest which contains the &lt;a href=\"Liquid%20Rainbow\"&gt;Liquid Rainbow&lt;/a&gt;, an item needed to enter the fabled &lt;a href=\"Whimsyshire\"&gt;Whimsyshire&lt;/a&gt;. Note that neither Zaven nor the chest are guaranteed to spawn. It may also spawn a Cursed Spire in which you have to fend off 5 waves of zombies. This is required in order to complete the Cursebreaker of Caldeum achievement.\nIn &lt;a href=\"Adventure%20Mode\"&gt;Adventure Mode&lt;/a&gt;, there is a chance \"Clear the Mysterious Cave\" will be one of the five Act II bounties. If so, Zaven is guaranteed to spawn."}
