{"id": "20995", "revid": "9305822", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=20995", "title": "Lamentation", "text": "Lamentation is a &lt;a href=\"Legendary%20Items\"&gt;legendary&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Mighty%20Belts\"&gt;mighty belt&lt;/a&gt; for the in &lt;a href=\"Diablo%20III\"&gt;Diablo III&lt;/a&gt;. It requires &lt;a href=\"character%20level\"&gt;character level&lt;/a&gt; 60 to drop.\nIt was the only belt in game to roll &lt;a href=\"Critical%20Hit\"&gt;Critical Hit&lt;/a&gt; Chance past Patch 2.0, and until Patch 2.1.\nThe unique affix allows &lt;a href=\"Rend\"&gt;Rend&lt;/a&gt; to stack twice on the same target. However, it only applies to the &lt;a href=\"Bleed\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; damage itself: other effects do not stack. It should also be noted that applying the second stack will not refresh the duration of the first stack. With Bloodbath rune, it allows \"three\" separate bleed effects to damage a single foe at a time: two stacks of Rend + independent Bloodbath stack.\nAs of patch 2.6.7a, it also increases the damage of Rend."}
