{"id": "16299", "revid": "3423357", "url": "https://diablo.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16299", "title": "Lamprey (magic suffix)", "text": "Lamprey is a &lt;a href=\"suffix\"&gt;suffix&lt;/a&gt; that can appear on &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;. It provides a moderate &lt;a href=\"Life%20Steal\"&gt;Life Steal&lt;/a&gt; bonus.\nIt can start spawning on items at &lt;a href=\"Item%20Level\"&gt;Item Level&lt;/a&gt; 55, but will not be able to spawn on all items until level 77. Some items also are not able to acquire full effect.\nThe steal comes from how much damage you do to the monster. So 5% Life Stolen will return 5% of the damage you do to a monster. Life steal only works on melee and physical ranged attacks.\nSome monsters and objects, like &lt;a href=\"Skeleton\"&gt;Skeleton&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"Fire%20Tower\"&gt;Fire Tower&lt;/a&gt;s, will not give life when attacked.\nStats.\n\"Can appear on:\" &lt;a href=\"Magic%20Items\"&gt;Magic Items&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rare%20Items\"&gt;Rare Items&lt;/a&gt;\n\"Is available on:\" &lt;a href=\"Melee%20Weapons\"&gt;Melee Weapons&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Circlets\"&gt;Circlets&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Rings\"&gt;Rings&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Amulets\"&gt;Amulets&lt;/a&gt;"}
